\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Moto ,}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Stay your hand,\u8221\'94 said Elrahet. \u8220\'93She\u8217\'92s who we\u8217\'92ve come to see.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Oh?\u8221\'94 said Pell. \u8220\'93Have you come to see me, or have you come to tell your people lies.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I told no lies.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Come, El, you\u8217\'92re old enough to know that when you leave out important details, that\u8217\'92s as good as lying.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Stand and stare.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You know I could kill you right now.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You would break our truce?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93No,\u8221\'94 said Pell. \u8220\'93But I must admit, there\u8217\'92s always that lingering thought, isn\u8217\'92t there, that if I were to kill you one more time, it would be the death that }{\f1\fs24\b0\i1 sticks}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 .\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Do you wish to return to those days, Pell?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I already said, no. But if you\u8217\'92ve come to my door to offer yourselves to the slaughter, I accept.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93One }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Excuse me, but who is this?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I see you have a new toy.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93It\u8217\'92s no toy,\u8221\'94 said Elrahet. \u8220\'93It\u8217\'92s as Sparked as you and me.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Pell\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s face went cold. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93There\u8217\'92s no end to your willingness to pervert the Spark, is there?\u8221\'94 Looks over Obo. Lips drawn tight, she muttered, \u8220\'93Abomination.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Abomination!? Speak of abomination\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 what about those poles in the Goree Pass!?\u8221\'94}
