\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Eyes alighted on Mandri, a smile of recognition. Mandri thought she was going to say him.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Gentle Sparks,\u8221\'94 she said aloud, throwing her voice out into the cavern, \u8220\'93Would you please grace us with your presence?\u8221\'94}
