\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93These demons, they want to kill me?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Nothing so crude. What they want to do is recover your Spark and add it to their own.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Obo, fang. Turned to Pell and said, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93That is not acceptable.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Stunned, tight lipped, then a burst of laughter, peal of.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Oh, how quaint! It\u8217\'92s not acceptable?! My dear Mazyd, we have collected an uncountable number of Sparks. You will be no different.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Of that uncountable number, how many could defend themselves with Mazydfire?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93We have collected the Sparks of gods. I assure you, you will be no different.\u8221\'94}
